                  </hi>. On 16th Oct., the prisoner came to me and told me he had truck or barrow to sell—he asked if I would buy it—I said I did not want anything of the kind, but he might bring it—he asked 12<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. for it—I bought it for 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—he said he wanted to buy a diamond, to go to work, and that would enable him to buy it—I sold the barrow again the same day for 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.</p>
